+signaling_handler::deferred_work signaling_handler::take_deferred()
+{
+	// Called while data_mutex is held. Moves out everything queued during this locked section,
+	// plus a snapshot of the context-id lists, so dispatch_deferred can run the callbacks (which
+	// resolve the contexts through idm and take the per-context lock) with data_mutex released.
